{"tid":492713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）好心提醒落車　巴士女司機反被乘客打荷包","createTime":"2017-12-07T20:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T14:00:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"81bdcdfda083048406ba471c475da5a50469735c","tid":492713,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T20:57:51.000Z","msg":"12月06日(三) 00:31 <br />\n東網電視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支那社會出現信任危機，真的不是沒原因。山東濟南一名巴士女司機，最近好心提醒睡過站的乘客下車，沒料到對方竟趁她買飯時，偷走了她的錢包，然後逃之夭夭。 <br />\n<br />\n陸姓女司機憶述，上周五（1日）下午，她開車抵達總站時，發現一名男乘客在車上睡着，於是好心提醒他落車，還教他如何換乘車輛至目的地。沒料到，該名乘客趁女司機落車後，返回巴士上偷走她的銀包。 <br />\n<br />\n陸司機表示，當時她看見男乘客下車後，因為實在太餓，所以未有鎖上車門就去買午飯，發現沒帶銀包才返回巴士，沒料到前後不到10秒時間，錢包就被偷走。不過令她窩心的是，當她和攤販說「不買了，我錢包丟了」時，攤販回答：「我賖給你吧。」 <br />\n<br />\n陸司機事後報警處理。她說，錢包裏有她辛苦賺來的2000元人民幣以及各種證件、銀行卡等，特別是還有駕駛證。她希望能夠及時找到這名乘客，並追回證件，否則將影響她的正常工作。"},{"pid":"115bd66754009591eaf1f9c81bbab23cccd767bd","tid":492713,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T20:59:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/mobile/bkncn-20171206003159829-1206_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171206003159829-1206_05011_001.html&d=VMhcE096Lzof%2B7AyFydcSJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5ef576d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/mobile/bkncn-20171206003159829-1206_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c131a24b3dbc7a02f8e43110049a730f2523841","tid":492713,"uid":106375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T21:20:13.000Z","msg":"乜支那唔係唔用現金嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985a719911539b3c54939e9cd52a5365fa4e3dad","tid":492713,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜支那唔係唔用現金嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買飯要用現金？？？？<br />\n<br />\n説好的先進呢？？？？"},{"pid":"0fed1c0787b3a2c1975d5ba69e022730226c9710","tid":492713,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477b0494493f93caddafec6fb1e5cb10214d6706","tid":492713,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1eb0c06c73b912763e7af86879a3346af68278","tid":492713,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"唔用QR CODE抵死啦"},{"pid":"72059f72595ac5fa91025f527fc5bdd50d8e4199","tid":492713,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"司機自己柒。。"},{"pid":"6e250de8b00a29414076629a302f55910b2f5ec0","tid":492713,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"咁好心做咩 話撚知佢瞓幾耐"},{"pid":"59903e2dfcfb196f64dd5b3abf74a6b0af11ae74","tid":492713,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"52b5eaaaccbfb51bea98fa5b45c0ac5c43ec0df1","tid":492713,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55399c7dd5053a3e0c0c507c162fd49f33015560","tid":492713,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:09:33.000Z","msg":"攤販回答：「我賖給你吧。」 <br />\n<br />\n給我爽一下就賒給你"},{"pid":"cb6362a18d94bde431f527d101818bcc7d619959","tid":492713,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68288e685ba9959b4f930667ae3dd423d3fd819","tid":492713,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:57:17.0